rComments: I really didn't like her as a prof.  She was clearly uncomfortable teaching and could not control the class (to the point where it got difficult to hear sometimes).  Her expectations for assignments was quite vague, even when asked to clarify.  Exams were fair, but the class was very tedious and I found myself drifting to Facebook a lot.

A very nice lady, but a tough professor. You really have to put in the work for assignments to get a good a grade. You can also tell that giving a lecture isn't quite in her comfort zone, as she gets a little nervous. Her exams however were very fair, and if you are ever confused at all she is more than willing to help you. She knows her stuff!
